lead_paragraph: The turn of the Olympic cycle has ushered in a new generation of riders plotting to overthrow track queen Anna Meares, but the seasoned Australian is confident of being in top gear to defend her sprint title at the Rio de Janeiro Games.

headline.print_headline: Sprint Queen Meares on Track for More Glory in Rio
